    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Reliable and ready to roll \u2014 a fantastic everyday driver at a wallet-friendly price! This car is in fair condition, meaning it's mechanically sound and gets you where you need to go dependably day after day. You'll notice some cosmetic wear and minor imperfections that come naturally with regular use, but nothing that affects its road-worthiness. If you're looking for practical, no-fuss transportation without breaking the bank, this is a great opportunity!",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
