      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Don't miss this exceptional opportunity to own a vehicle in truly mint condition! This car has been meticulously maintained and it absolutely shows \u2014 the exterior gleams without a scratch or blemish, and the interior is fresh, clean, and feels nearly new. Everything works exactly as it should, and you'll be hard-pressed to find another example this well-preserved on the market. If you've been searching for a top-quality vehicle you can be proud of from day one, this is the one!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront so you can make a well-informed decision. The exterior is in rough shape \u2014 expect heavy rust on multiple body panels, deep scratches and dents throughout, and faded, peeling paint that has lost most of its protective quality. The interior is similarly worn, with torn and stained upholstery, a cracked dashboard, and several non-functional components including climate controls and power accessories. Mechanically, the car runs but requires significant attention \u2014 there are known issues with the engine that cause rough idling and occasional stalling, the transmission shifts inconsistently, and the brakes are due for immediate replacement. Suspension components are worn and the ride is noticeably rough. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a major restoration project or someone looking for a parts source. It is not recommended for daily driving in its current state without substantial repairs first.",
      "price": 3500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude99 Honest Value & Ready to Ride \u2013 A Practical Fair-Condition Gem! \ud83d\ude99\n\nLooking for a dependable vehicle that won't break the bank? This could be your match! We'll be completely upfront with you: this car is in fair condition, meaning it has some visible wear and minor imperfections that come with a well-used vehicle \u2014 but it runs and gets you where you need to go! It's a solid choice for budget-conscious buyers who want reliable transportation without the premium price tag. What you see is what you get, and at this price, it's a genuinely great value for the right buyer. Come take a look \u2014 we'd love to find this car a good home! \ud83d\ude4c",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely upfront with you about what that means. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 the paint is faded, scratched, and has areas of visible rust or damage that go beyond cosmetic concerns. The interior is worn with tears, staining, and damage to multiple surfaces. Mechanically, this car has known issues that will require attention; it may run but should not be considered reliable transportation without repair work. This listing is priced accordingly for a buyer who is comfortable with a project vehicle, a parts car, or someone with the skills and budget to bring it back to roadworthy condition. Please inspect thoroughly before purchasing \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we encourage you to factor in repair costs before committing.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a poor-condition car, best suited for buyers on a very tight budget, those seeking a project vehicle, or anyone who needs minimal point-A-to-point-B transportation and can handle some ongoing maintenance. The exterior shows heavy wear throughout \u2014 expect noticeable rust, dents, scratches, and faded or peeling paint that significantly detract from its appearance. The interior is worn and tired, with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general neglect visible throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car runs but is not without issues \u2014 prospective buyers should anticipate the need for repairs, and a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic is strongly recommended before committing. There are no luxury features to speak of, and reliability cannot be guaranteed for long trips or heavy daily use. This listing is priced to reflect the car's true condition, and what you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises, just honest value for the right buyer.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    }
